<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٤٩٨٤ - وَكِيعٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْأَعْمَشِ قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُهُمْ يَذْكُرُونَ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ شُرَيْحٍ:</span> أَنَّهُ <span class="c1">" رَأَى جِيرَانًا لَهُ تَحَوَّلُوا ,<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> مَا لَكُمْ؟<span class="c5"> قَالُوا:</span> فَزِعْنَا ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَبِهَذَا أَمْرُ الْفَزَعِ "</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>